longBusinessSummary: Authentic Holdings, Inc. operates in fan wear and memorabilia industries. The company creates and distributes vinyl records to retail department stores, as well as online; and operates NFT platform. It also focuses on providing branded fabrics, apparels, and uniforms to the corporate, hotel, hospital, and military markets. The company was formerly known as Global Fiber Technologies, Inc. Authentic Holdings, Inc. was founded in 2004 and is based in Somerset, New Jersey.
